Value PORT (\S+)
Value POE_STATUS (Delivering|Searching|Disabled|Fault)
Value POWER_MW (\d+\.?\d*)
Value PRIORITY (low|high|critical)
Value CLASS (\d+)

Start
  ^---+ -> PoEData

PoEData
  ^${PORT}\s+${POE_STATUS}\s+${POWER_MW}\s+${PRIORITY}\s+${CLASS}\s*$$ -> Record
  ^${PORT}\s+${POE_STATUS}\s+${POWER_MW}\s+${PRIORITY}\s*$$ -> Record
